{"root":{"data":{"id":"djuyievb6hs0","created":1783693319670,"text":"EGCN++：基于骨架的康复训练评估的集成学习新融合策略"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djuyluv89h40","created":1783693589586,"text":"摘要"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djuym25a3f40","created":1783693605432,"text":"研究背景"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djuymc6f0j40","created":1783693627268,"text":"基于骨骼的锻炼评估侧重于评估受试者所做动作的正确性或质量"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djuymg1r36o0","created":1783693635693,"text":"现有的方法未能充分利用骨骼数据提供的两组特征（即位置和方向）"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djuym2bpj800","created":1783693605820,"text":"研究发现"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djuymkf33q00","created":1783693645207,"text":"本文提出了一个名为EGCN++的先进框架，其中提出了一种新的融合策略MLE-PO，该策略考虑了数据和模型层面的融合"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djuylvgdxig0","created":1783693590866,"text":"研究方向"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djuymskft540","created":1783693662944,"text":"物理治疗师经常使用康复锻炼来帮助恢复和预防各种肌肉骨骼疾病"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djuylvkv4bc0","created":1783693591136,"text":"实验结果"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djuylvujxsg0","created":1783693591722,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djuylw34z1c0","created":1783693592241,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djuylw88b7c0","created":1783693592549,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}